# Paper A manifests: raw third-party row text (ToxicChat CC-BY-NC, gated AI2,
# etc.) must not be redistributed under this repo's Apache-2.0 license
# (plan sec 6.2 Branch A). The .jsonl row files stay local; the auditable,
# text-free artifacts (manifest.json, audit/) remain tracked.
/artifacts/**/manifests/*.jsonl

